                  <h2>Ownership History</h2>
      <p>William Sumner Appleton, Boston, from 1871 to 1903; by descent to William Sumner Appleton, Jr., Boston, from 1903. C.C. Childes, Boston, by 1941; sold to The Art Institute of Chicago, 1942.</p>
